reflinks-autogen: A short identifier for autogenerated reference titles
reflinks-comment: A hint what the bot adds between when converts bare references. Preceded by the title, so this message means "title which is generated by bot".
reflinks-msg:
Edit summary when the bot places a title for a bare html link inside references
* %(manual)s - a interlanguage link to the bot's localized manual, usually [[mw:Manual:Pywikibot/refLinks]]
